========================================
6 HARD CONSTRAINTS - ALL ACTIVE
========================================

1. ‚úÖ CONSTRAINT 1: Exact Shift Fulfillment
   - Every medewerker gets EXACTLY required shifts
   - Status: DOCUMENTED & ENFORCED

2. ‚úÖ CONSTRAINT 2: No Overlapping Shifts
   - One medewerker cannot work two shifts simultaneously
   - Status: DOCUMENTED & ENFORCED

3. ‚úÖ CONSTRAINT 3: Shift Preferences Honored
   - Respect mijn_voorkeur and swap_preference flags
   - Status: DOCUMENTED & ENFORCED

4. ‚úÖ CONSTRAINT 4: Fair Distribution
   - Max deviation = 20% of average shifts
   - Status: DOCUMENTED & ENFORCED

5. ‚úÖ CONSTRAINT 5: Blackout Dates Honored
   - Do NOT assign shifts on unavailability dates
   - Status: DOCUMENTED & ENFORCED

6. ‚úÖ CONSTRAINT 6: Coverage Requirements Met
   - Every day must have minimum required coverage
   - Status: DOCUMENTED & ENFORCED

========================================
ARCHITECTURE IMPLEMENTATION
========================================

Greedy Selection Algorithm:
  FOR each week_date
    FOR each dagdeel (OCHTEND, MIDDAG, NACHT)
      WHILE shifts_available
        1. GET eligible medewerkers
        2. SCORE (fairness + preference + availability)
        3. ASSIGN highest-scored medewerker
        4. VERIFY all 6 constraints
        5. BACKTRACK if violated

Database Tables Integrated:
  - rooster (main planning)
  - medewerker (personnel)
  - planning_requirements (shift requirements)
  - planning_detail (preferences)
  - medewerker_unavailability (blackout dates)
  - planning_constraints (config)

